## ğŸš€ **Quick Start**

### Development
```bash
git clone <repo>
cp .env.example .env
npm install
npm run dev
```

### Production with Docker
```bash
docker-compose up -d
# Access at http://localhost:3000
```

### Kubernetes Deployment
```bash
chmod +x kubernetes/auto-scaling.sh
./kubernetes/auto-scaling.sh
```

